  "final_answer": "Fever can be addressed with natural ingredients, including honey, which contains compounds like glucose and fructose. Honey's key compounds, glucose and fructose, have been linked to several drugs, including Glucose, which is identically mapped to the drug compound Glucose in Iveegam EN, and Fructose, which is identically mapped to the drug compound Fructose in Eraxis.\n\nAccording to a Hadith, \"Fever is from the heat of the (Hell) Fire, so cool it with water,\" as narrated by Aisha. Another Hadith mentions using Zamzam water to cool fever. However, there is no specific Hadith that mentions grapes as a cure for fever.\n\nPlease consult a healthcare professional before using any natural ingredients or drugs to treat fever, as they can provide personalized advice and ensure safe treatment.",
